001package com.commercetools.graphql.api.client;
002
003import com.commercetools.graphql.api.types.StagedQuoteDraft;
004import com.netflix.graphql.dgs.client.codegen.GraphQLQuery;
005import java.lang.Override;
006import java.lang.String;
007import java.util.HashSet;
008import java.util.Set;
009
010public class CreateStagedQuoteGraphQLQuery extends GraphQLQuery {
011  public CreateStagedQuoteGraphQLQuery(StagedQuoteDraft draft, String queryName,
012      Set<String> fieldsSet) {
013    super("mutation", queryName);
014    if (draft != null || fieldsSet.contains("draft")) {
015        getInput().put("draft", draft);
016    }
017  }
018
019  public CreateStagedQuoteGraphQLQuery() {
020    super("mutation");
021  }
022
023  @Override
024  public String getOperationName() {
025     return "createStagedQuote";
026                    
027  }
028
029  public static Builder newRequest() {
030    return new Builder();
031  }
032
033  public static class Builder {
034    private Set<String> fieldsSet = new HashSet<>();
035
036    private StagedQuoteDraft draft;
037
038    private String queryName;
039
040    public CreateStagedQuoteGraphQLQuery build() {
041      return new CreateStagedQuoteGraphQLQuery(draft, queryName, fieldsSet);
042               
043    }
044
045    public Builder draft(StagedQuoteDraft draft) {
046      this.draft = draft;
047      this.fieldsSet.add("draft");
048      return this;
049    }
050
051    public Builder queryName(String queryName) {
052      this.queryName = queryName;
053      return this;
054    }
055  }
056}
